Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you last change shafts?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Six days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,After the clean-up operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That matches the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Krista Lenz, Squad 42.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it for wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought killing Titans was a punishable offense...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}does{\i0} seem ironic, but those two were valuable test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, why are they looking for the culprit among us trainees?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.01,0:02:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We just finished cleaning up the battlefield today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's totally beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit must've really loathed the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But in reality, they ended up helping the Titans...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They may have fulfilled their personal desire for vengeance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but the net result is a major setback for humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I get why they did it, because I can be an idiot myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I'd ever seen a Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was certain I wanted to join the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I never want to see another.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And today, we all have to decide which force to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even Jean's seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone's regretting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I'd known it'd be this hellish,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd have never chosen to be a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I'm so exhausted,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't think of anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Marco...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even tell which are your bones anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I hadn't become a soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wouldn't have to keep wondering who'll be on that pile next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we abandon the tactical progress bought by tens of thousands of sacrifices,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,just to serve ourselves up on a silver platter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:04:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know we have to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But not everyone's as eager to die as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you won't get upset when I say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But you aren't a strong person, Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can relate to the feelings of the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, you excel at sizing up any situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why you already know what needs to be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What needs to be done...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you decided which force you're joining?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm joining the Recon Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Annie. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Jean said he's joining the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Jean said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joining the Military Police, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone told you to die, would you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why not make your own decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think if you know why you have to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,there are times when you must lay down your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You've made your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking it over for quite a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? Armin, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weak, but you've got guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie, you're actually pretty nice, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like you don't want us to join the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a reason you want to join the Military Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they couldn't find any soldiers who used
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,their Maneuver Gear without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm more worried about the upcoming induction ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How many of the new cadets are actually crazy enough to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:07:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any people in your class who'd join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there {\i1}were{\i0} some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going out on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Captain Levi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Never stray more than two horse-lengths from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that the only reason
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not locked up is because I'm watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really joining the Recon Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the sudden choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I don't {\i1}want{\i0}  to join the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that the Titans don't scare me anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't spout nonsense like, "The best belong in the Recon Corps."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not as eager to die as some are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already joined the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Trainees, line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Line up in front of the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Line up in front of the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not risking my life because someone convinced me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a job you can't do unless you decide for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Erwin Smith, Commander of the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you will choose a branch of the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting it bluntly, I'm here to persuade you to join the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,During their recent attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you learned how terrifying the Titans can be,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as how limited your own strength is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That battle brought mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,closer to victory than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger's existence is crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,By risking his own life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,he's undoubtedly proven himself a great ally to mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,With his help, not only did we stop the Titans' advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but we've also obtained a key to discovering their true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe that the basement of his old home in Shiganshina
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,holds answers about the Titans that even he doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can reach that basement,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we will find clues to ending this century of Titan domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already advanced that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If we learn what they are, we can end this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how much he needs recruits,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe he's publicizing this information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or does he have some hidden motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We will head for the basement in Shiganshina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}However, that requires us to retake Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}In other words, our objective remains the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But with the Trost gate sealed for good,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}we'll have to take the long way around from Karanes in the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The four years we spent laying a route
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}for a full-scale army have gone to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}In those four years, more than sixty percent of the Recon Corps lost their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sixty percent in four years...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}An insane figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Any trainees who join us will participate in our excursion beyond the walls next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We expect thirty percent won't return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In four years, most will be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But those who make it through
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,will become superior soldiers with a high survival rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you know the discouraging facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Any of you still willing to risk your lives, remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask yourselves:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to offer your beating hearts for mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who wishes to join another branch is dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you scared them a little much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them will leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, you've already made your choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't give me more reasons to hate myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't leave now, I'll have to face them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I left the village to join the Military Police...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mom would be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I join the Military Police, the whole village would think better of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We all know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've already seen it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How the Titans...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...devour humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all willing to die if you're ordered to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the looks on your faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby welcome all of you to the Recon Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a true salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Offer up your hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the pits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Recon Corps...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were going to cry, you should have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well to endure your fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You are brave soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my heartfelt respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Squad Leader Ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is Shallot, my horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She loves to chew on people's hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so be careful or you'll wind up prematurely bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! S-Stop it, Shallot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone grab her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our training began the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of practical training, it was mostly memorizing the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,long-range scouting formation Commander Erwin had devised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Strangely,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,although the formation was written out in precise detail,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger's position was nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You new recruits will be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in between the recon support team
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and the supply wagon escort team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your jobs will be to ride alongside the \Nspare horses and relay messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Special Operations Squad will be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,standing by in the center of the last ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're pretty far back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the safest place in the formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're even more heavily guarded than the supply wagons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our goal this time is just to sortie and return safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This expedition is so brief
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's a practice run for your journey to Shiganshina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know what this power should be used for...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you understand what the Commander's question meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where do you think the enemy is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you all understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be an overstatement to say I understand it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible this mission has another goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Commander has decided it'd be best not to reveal that objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So we should just focus on getting there and back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just believe in the Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the training for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to return to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, may I go talk with my classmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mikasa! Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like it's been forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, did they do anything bad to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they examine you all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they psychologically torture you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That midget bastard crossed the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I'll make him pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean Captain Levi, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Everyone's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're all here, then—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean all of you joined the Recon Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else would we be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So only Jean, Annie, and Marco joined the Military Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Not you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say Marco's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everyone goes out in a blaze of glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know how it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He died without anyone around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, newbies! Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uniforms are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we'll all be participating in the mission too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that when you turned into a Titan, you tried to kill Mikasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Eren was trying to hit a fly—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa, that wound on your cheek looks pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm told it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When I became a Titan, I tried to kill Mikasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So then you don't remember it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you didn't even know you had this Titan power,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and you still don't have the means to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you all hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind's existence, and our lives, depend on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll probably die just like Marco,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,without Eren even noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean, what's the point in asking Eren these questions now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Mikasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everyone's like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,willing to die for Eren's sake and nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We deserve to know what we're dying for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, we'll hesitate when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We want something in return from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what he has to offer us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And whether it's worth our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're {\i1}really{\i0}  counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We've driven all the Titans out of the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty seconds until we open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Recon Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They call that emblem on their backs the Wings of Freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity will take another step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me what you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.09,0:22:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now begin the 57th \Nexpedition beyond the walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Onward!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Entering long-range scouting formation,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the Recon Corps advances beyond the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:24:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, they suddenly find themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,facing down a mysteriously intelligent Titan.
