Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:08.70,Op 2 - TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(200,200)\blur1}O, my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:13.90,Op 2 - TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(200,200)\blur1}Let us celebrate this victory for the next battle!
