Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:45.40,Op 2 - TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(200,200)\blur1}The enemy is colossal... We will jump—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.36,0:00:49.04,Op 2 - TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(200,200)\blur1}In our hands we hold blades of glory
