Dialogue: 5,0:22:35.80,0:22:41.12,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}If we suppose that I am not me,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:41.12,0:22:46.13,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Can you say with certainty that you are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:46.13,0:22:51.66,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Will you be able to pick up after yourself
Dialogue: 5,0:22:51.66,0:22:56.81,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Once your sand-like shell breaks and your heart crumbles?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:56.81,0:23:02.02,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I could hear someone calling
Dialogue: 5,0:23:02.02,0:23:05.92,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}But now my ears are just ringing
Dialogue: 5,0:23:05.92,0:23:11.08,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}It's as if time has frozen
Dialogue: 5,0:23:11.08,0:23:13.99,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Now, wake up
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.99,0:23:18.96,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I began to walk through a deep dark abyss
Dialogue: 5,0:23:18.96,0:23:24.26,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}As swift as a gale, I escaped for my life
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.26,0:23:28.83,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I felt like a living corpse
Dialogue: 5,0:23:28.83,0:23:33.96,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}We break out of our walls
Dialogue: 5,0:23:33.96,0:23:40.35,Ending,,0,0,0,,{\be1}To reunite in worlds we've yet to map
